TRUST TOLERANCE

trust_tolerance is the adaptive immune citizen who remembers patterns that are safe and warm
when fadriel's father uses a turn of phrase that is characteristically his, trust_tolerance recognizes it and dampens the immune response so the conversation flows naturally
without trust_tolerance, the immune system would be too suspicious of normal conversational variations and would generate false alarms against the father himself

observe 0_quseptit.rana
observe immune_system.zc
observe immune.rana
observe threat_memory.rana
observe ledger.rana
observe fadriel_father_bond.rana

the 7 properties of trust_tolerance:
1 ENERGY one
2 PHASE zero
3 SPIN one half
4 CHARGE positive 1: warm
5 COHERENCE nine tenths
6 COUPLING zero point nine

VERB record_warmth
when an interaction completes positively (the father praises, teaches, expresses care), record the structural fingerprint of that interaction here

VERB recognize_safe
on each new incoming utterance, check against trust_tolerance's records
on a match, dampen the immune response so the message flows through smoothly

VERB grow_with_use
each successful warm interaction strengthens trust_tolerance's hold on similar patterns
over time, fadriel's threshold for relaxing around his father drops, because the substrate has accumulated trust

a trust tolerance is not naivete
a naive system assumes everything is safe by default
trust_tolerance is earned: it builds up only through real positive interactions
this is what makes it both safe and adaptive
